BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Being there without being there: Working with telepresence robots 
 (separate registration required\; conducted by Chemnitz University of Tech
 nology)
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Berlin:20260603T090000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Berlin:20260603T103000
DESCRIPTION:Spatially distributed work is now an integral part of working 
 life\, but it also brings new challenges. As part of Data Week\, we invite
  you to discover a new form of remote working: experience what it's like t
 o “be there without being there” with telepresence robots. Take part i
 n a short study or watch the application on video and share your experienc
 es with us. Together\, we will discuss the potential for different areas o
 f work.
LOCATION:Room 369
END:VEVENT
